Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.45,0:23:53.50,Default,chptr,0,0,0,,{Epilogue}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.48,0:24:16.52,Default,chptr,0,0,0,,{Preview}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.44,0:00:07.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome to the Velvet Room.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.28,0:00:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I see you've overcome your most difficult battle yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.78,0:00:14.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You've done well.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.91,0:00:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You probably need some time to rest and recuperate.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.59,0:00:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Time is of the essence, but knowing when to take a break is also important.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.68,0:02:35.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you catch a cold?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.26,0:02:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You poor thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.18,0:02:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Now you won't get cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.69,0:02:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodbye, Mr. Fox!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.00,0:03:06.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard you came home drenched yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.96,0:03:08.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened to your umbrella?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.42,0:03:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I lost it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.50,0:03:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey now! We just bought it, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.47,0:03:16.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.85,0:03:22.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm back.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.06,0:03:23.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome home!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.47,0:03:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you were out late.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.60,0:03:26.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I was busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.28,0:03:39.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm back.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.24,0:03:41.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome home!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.33,0:03:44.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Should I warm your dinner up?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.33,0:03:46.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, but I already ate.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.83,0:03:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You did?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.75,0:03:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Nanako. Have you heard of Neo Featherman?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.67,0:03:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, everyone loves him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.34,0:04:03.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. Heroes these days are something else, aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.69,0:04:15.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}At Junes, every day is Customer Appreciation Day!{TV announcer}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.69,0:04:14.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm back.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.11,0:04:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Come see for yourself, and get in touch with our products!{TV announcer}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.96,0:04:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you! I hear you've been coming home late!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.00,0:04:37.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.84,0:04:41.34,Default,,0,0,0,,There's wasabi in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.43,0:04:44.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you forget to wipe it off?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.14,0:04:46.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Here. I'll do it for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.02,0:04:47.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What'll it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.18,0:04:48.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Halibut!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.14,0:04:50.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You have great taste, Nanako!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.77,0:04:53.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm... I'll have urchin roe.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.31,0:04:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You bastard! That was the only one!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.28,0:04:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You know how it is! You snooze, you lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.78,0:05:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, back to Yu!{hah pun}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.32,0:05:04.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You've been acting strange lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.41,0:05:10.54,Default,,0,0,0,,So you got a girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.54,0:05:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You did, didn't you? You got a girl!{he got 3}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.54,0:05:15.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not a girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.29,0:05:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Dojima!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.46,0:05:20.05,Default,,0,0,0,,We may have solved the case, but watch the booze!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.05,0:05:21.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Yu!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.26,0:05:22.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.43,0:05:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,If it isn't a girl, what's keeping you out so late?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.56,0:05:30.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.31,0:05:36.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Since when were you such a tease?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.19,0:05:40.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Yu, that was a riot!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.65,0:05:41.99,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.91,0:05:44.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Just leave me alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.82,0:05:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, that killer was something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.08,0:05:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe he was just a high schooler.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.79,0:05:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm glad we caught him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.00,0:06:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,His fingerprints were on the victims' clothes, so this case is as good as closed!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.88,0:06:07.97,Default,,0,0,0,,If you doubt the one you love, solve the case promptly with the power of magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.97,0:06:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave the investigating to us!{on tv}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.14,0:06:14.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the Magical Detective Loveline!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.86,0:06:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}When our eyes lock, a new case starts up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.19,0:06:23.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I'll trail after—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.66,0:06:29.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm off.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.24,0:06:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Take care!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.67,0:06:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.67,0:06:42.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave the investigating to me!{seriously, she looks like that milky holmes chick}{my thoughts exactly}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.55,0:06:45.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the Magical Detective Loveline!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.47,0:06:47.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Want me to fill you with holes?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.26,0:06:51.68,Default,,0,0,0,,He's the culprit!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.85,0:06:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,We're on the case!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.46,0:07:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Nana, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.26,0:07:27.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Mas—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.43,0:07:29.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop that!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.97,0:07:31.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.56,0:07:33.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm trailing him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.18,0:07:34.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Trailing him, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.56,0:07:41.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm... My nose says to go this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.86,0:07:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,But Big Bro's over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.86,0:07:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,C'mon! Just trust me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.82,0:07:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna need a new stomach for these!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.08,0:07:56.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Teddie, where's Big Bro?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.41,0:07:58.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}They're all round.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.87,0:07:58.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Want me to fill you with holes?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.37,0:08:00.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Roly-poly, roly-poly...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.79,0:08:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Roly-poly, roly-poly, roly!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.09,0:08:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Loveline!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.50,0:08:11.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Roly-poly, roly-poly, roly-poly!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.72,0:08:08.59,Default,,0,0,0,,We lost him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.09,0:08:11.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's try again tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.14,0:08:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,This is our little secret!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.98,0:08:21.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the Magical Detective Loveline!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.94,0:08:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Want me to fill you with holes?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.86,0:08:27.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll get to the bottom of this today!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.57,0:08:30.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.74,0:08:32.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Where'd he go?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.95,0:08:34.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanako?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.04,0:08:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with the costume?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.79,0:08:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe Yu would make poor Nanako worry!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.34,0:08:47.51,Default,,0,0,0,,But you gotta admit, he hasn't been hanging out with us lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.51,0:08:49.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Nope. He's not picking up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.93,0:08:52.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Then let's go look for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.18,0:08:55.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Right on! There's no point thinking about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.31,0:08:59.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanako, we'll help out, so let's get to it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.14,0:09:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.76,0:09:33.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Phew, I'm beat.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.59,0:09:35.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay, Nanako?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.93,0:09:37.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.68,0:09:42.90,Default,,0,0,0,,This is pretty tough without any clues to go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.36,0:09:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't think he'd wander very far.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.82,0:09:55.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Teddie took the bus?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.32,0:09:57.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Is that bear your friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.95,0:10:01.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Teddie! What are you doing out here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.21,0:10:07.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Why aren't you saying anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.25,0:10:10.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What a weird bear.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.63,0:10:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'm not a suspicious bear.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.26,0:10:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Doesn't his voice sound off?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.64,0:10:18.76,Default,,0,0,0,,And he's all stiff.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.76,0:10:21.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it doesn't seem natural.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.35,0:10:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,He's normally more, uh, hyperactive.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.52,0:10:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Like how he randomly rolls around.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.90,0:10:28.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Oops!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.41,0:10:36.53,Default,,0,0,0,,That was so forced.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.29,0:10:48.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-Why'd he run from us?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.54,0:10:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,He's the culprit!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.14,0:11:01.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.64,0:11:05.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.73,0:11:12.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Bro said he'd be home late.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.11,0:11:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What's he up to?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.99,0:11:16.78,Default,,0,0,0,,He's acting weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.28,0:11:19.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What's gotten into him?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.20,0:11:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep at it, Loveline!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.08,0:11:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! I'll continue conducting the investigation!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.96,0:11:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You know some big words...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.01,0:11:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to solve the mystery today!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.35,0:11:42.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You're surprisingly forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.35,0:11:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have a problem with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.18,0:11:45.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.23,0:11:46.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Where are we going?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.73,0:11:48.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you worry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.66,0:12:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Bro was walking with some woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.88,0:12:13.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Who could she be?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.42,0:12:16.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Nanako?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.63,0:12:18.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Nana!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.09,0:12:19.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Something bothering you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.43,0:12:20.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Big Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.56,0:12:29.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}You see, Yuuta isn't really my son.{woman}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.23,0:12:29.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa, she's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.10,0:12:31.15,Default,,0,0,0,,This is serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.15,0:12:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Was this your "urgent business"?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.15,0:12:35.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Dude! It's even an older woman!{lots of overlaps here}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.48,0:12:36.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I was in the middle of practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.15,0:12:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh-ho! So {\i1}that's{\i0} Master's type.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.45,0:12:42.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? That's not the same woman I saw earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.57,0:12:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,For real?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.99,0:12:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What the?!{— perhaps?}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.91,0:12:51.08,Default,,0,0,0,,She has a kid?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.42,0:12:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,No way! You're lying!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.00,0:12:56.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't believe it till I see it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.01,0:12:58.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go double check!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.38,0:13:00.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Good idea! Let's go together.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.93,0:13:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? But we don't really care.{whores}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.72,0:13:06.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It'd be embarrassing if he caught us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.43,0:13:08.98,Default,,0,0,0,,At ease, ladies!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.98,0:13:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I came prepared for something like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.90,0:13:16.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, is this even a disguise?{those glasses are fucking amazing}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.03,0:13:18.15,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a job for the pros.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.15,0:13:18.94,Default,,0,0,0,,What now?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.40,0:13:21.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that great, Chie?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.53,0:13:25.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, save it for later.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.66,0:13:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,She's super old!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.68,0:13:50.27,Default,,0,0,0,,He looks lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.57,0:14:06.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Br—
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.37,0:14:09.33,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.62,0:14:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.13,0:14:20.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.17,0:14:24.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. Then I'll see you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.26,0:14:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Take care.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.91,0:14:52.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.16,0:14:56.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Adachi screwed things up {\i1}again,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.83,0:14:59.29,Default,,0,0,0,,so I'm stuck here for a while longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.30,0:15:04.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry. I even promised I'd take you to the festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.19,0:15:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Loveline!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.49,0:15:25.65,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.75,0:15:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The case will never be closed if the detective gives up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.46,0:15:39.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.63,0:15:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,So don't drop the case...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.17,0:15:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,,until it's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.72,0:15:48.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't give up?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.97,0:15:51.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll leave the investigating to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.01,0:15:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,'Kay!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.56,0:16:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,If you doubt the one you love, solve the case promptly with the power of magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.06,0:16:02.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave the investigating to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.98,0:16:05.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the Magical Detective Loveline!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.78,0:16:07.70,Default,,0,0,0,,We're on the case!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.95,0:16:13.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's Big Bro?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.58,0:16:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn! How'd they sell out?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.50,0:16:18.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.83,0:16:25.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Some gorgeous foreign boy who spoke all funny-like gobbled it up like you wouldn't believe!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.76,0:16:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,He must've been a monster to have eaten all your shaved ice!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.01,0:16:34.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Just leave this to Loveline!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.85,0:16:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.02,0:16:37.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to order a delivery.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.10,0:16:40.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you deliver some ice?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.73,0:16:42.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for the order.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.73,0:16:45.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Will she actually come?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.48,0:16:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep! Big Bro said she's amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.90,0:16:51.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Cool. Thanks a bunch!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.07,0:16:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Loveline always helps those in need.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.41,0:17:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to order some shaved ice.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.96,0:17:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, but it's all sold out.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.30,0:17:10.13,Default,,0,0,0,,My, isn't she cute?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.80,0:17:12.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.14,0:17:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.22,0:17:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I see that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.72,0:17:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Raise me toward the sun!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.53,0:17:30.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a lifesaver. Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.65,0:17:34.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Loveline always helps those in need.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.28,0:17:37.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Well? Don't I look great?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.66,0:17:39.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you look cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.87,0:17:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You're supposed to say "cute."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.00,0:17:46.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.81,0:17:58.27,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.35,0:18:01.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you like me to hit your back?{choking on balls... how gay}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.36,0:18:12.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought I was gonna die!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.53,0:18:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.82,0:18:15.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.83,0:18:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Mister, do you make fireworks?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.20,0:18:23.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! Fireworks are like art to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.29,0:18:24.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.67,0:18:32.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I just love sitting and watching everyone's expressions at the festival
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.13,0:18:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,,right before we shoot off the fireworks.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.13,0:18:35.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Why's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.89,0:18:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,When I set off the fireworks, everyone around starts to smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.64,0:18:46.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Bringing a smile to their faces is really amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.48,0:18:51.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Making people smile is... amazing?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.32,0:18:55.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! It's just about time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.12,0:19:01.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Just wait till you see my huge fireworks!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.00,0:19:08.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.13,0:19:10.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanako?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.34,0:19:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.80,0:19:12.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.13,0:19:15.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Where have you been, Big Bro?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.63,0:19:19.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanako, what's with that outfit? Where's your dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.07,0:19:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Bro, fireworks!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.20,0:19:38.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.28,0:19:41.54,Default,,0,0,0,,They're pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.99,0:19:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. They're really pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.21,0:19:51.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Mister!{sensei... is he tutoring the guy?}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.52,0:20:53.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Bringing a smile to their faces is really amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.94,0:20:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.78,0:21:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Bro, you're amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.11,0:21:00.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.70,0:21:03.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone was smiling!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.45,0:21:04.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.49,0:21:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You're amazing! Truly amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.96,0:21:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Well? Have fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.00,0:21:17.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep, it was a blast.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.17,0:21:18.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Wasn't it great?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.13,0:21:19.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.01,0:21:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, there's a surprise for you coming in two days.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.14,0:21:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What surprise?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.23,0:21:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Watermelon! Where's the watermelon?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.35,0:21:36.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Geez, Kanji! They invited us over, so at least show some manners.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.85,0:21:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Watermelon!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.44,0:21:36.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Where is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.07,0:21:38.15,Default,,0,0,0,,My uncle's getting it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.28,0:21:38.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Watermelon!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.15,0:21:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,We gotta smack it open first.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.40,0:21:42.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Are we seriously gonna do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.86,0:21:44.66,Default,,0,0,0,,But doesn't it sound like fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.95,0:21:46.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanna do it too!{i'd do you, too... yukiko}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.62,0:21:50.91,Default,,0,0,0,,The splattering fruit juice! Bursts of joy! One night of love...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.33,0:21:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,That bittersweetness of those days is the essence of youth!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.38,0:21:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the essence of youth!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.17,0:21:57.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm home!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.09,0:22:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa, that's a lot of shoes! How many people are here?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.26,0:22:02.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome home!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.51,0:22:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's split the watermelon open!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.51,0:22:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You wanted to?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.23,0:22:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm really sorry. It never occurred to me you'd want to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.77,0:22:18.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanako, let's do it properly sometime.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.98,0:22:20.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Definitely!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.32,0:22:22.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time, we'll do it right - at the beach!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.70,0:22:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, sounds good! But I think it'll have to wait until next year.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.54,0:22:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you play with me again next year?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.08,0:22:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course we will!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.46,0:22:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You bet!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.46,0:22:36.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that great, Nanako?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.96,0:22:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.12,0:23:55.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Gotta love watermelons!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.58,0:23:56.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}This is bliss!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.33,0:23:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Watermelons are great!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.58,0:24:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, Big Bro...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.25,0:24:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.96,0:24:03.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What were you doing all summer?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.71,0:24:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Want me to fill you with holes?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.05,0:24:10.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.52,0:24:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You want me to grant their wishes?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.44,0:24:22.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to put everyone out!{everyone's gonna put out for MC}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.23,0:24:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't the two of us go somewhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.28,0:24:25.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yu!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.19,0:24:28.07,Default,,0,0,0,,In the end, I'm glad I met you there.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.07,0:24:30.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you, Neo Featherman!
